title: 'Love Is Blind' Episodes 1-3 Breakdown
description:
Amelia Wedemeyer and Juliet Litman sit down to talk about the explosive new season of 'Live Is Blind' on Netflix. They break down the first three episodes, including all the love triangles, problematic couples, and who they think will make it to the altar.
Hosts: Amelia Wedemeyer and Juliet Litman
Producers: Steve Ahlman and Chelsea Stark-Jones
